author: maintainer-agent
acceptance_criteria: tests/integration/claude-plugin-contract.spec.ts (or scripts/smoke-claude-plugin.mjs) reads .agents/plugins/marketplace.json and asserts its plugin list and version stay consistent with plugins/*/.codex-plugin/plugin.json and plugins/*/.claude-plugin/plugin.json; CI fails if the manifest drifts.
